      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Distribuzione dati per testata e righe      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   dda-fcs-wtr-000      thru dda-fcs-wtr-999        .
       rou-let-reg-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     rou-let-reg-999.
       rou-let-reg-900.
